## 🌐 WebSocket و Real-time Communication

### WebSocket Configuration
```java
@Configuration
@EnableWebSocket
public class WebSocketConfig implements WebSocketConfigurer {

    @Override
    public void registerWebSocketHandlers(WebSocketHandlerRegistry registry) {
        registry.addHandler(rawWebSocketHandler(), "/raw-ws")
                .setAllowedOriginPatterns("*");
    }

    @Bean
    public WebSocketHandler rawWebSocketHandler() {
        return new WebSocketHandler() {
            @Override
            public void afterConnectionEstablished(WebSocketSession session) {
                // Connection established logic
            }

            @Override
            public void handleMessage(WebSocketSession session, WebSocketMessage<?> message) {
                // Message handling logic
            }
        };
    }
}
```

### WebSocket Message Handling
```java
@Controller
@RequiredArgsConstructor
public class WebSocketController {

    private final WebSocketRoomService webSocketRoomService;

    @MessageMapping("/game/action")
    public void handleGameAction(@Payload WebSocketMessage message) {
        String action = message.getAction();
        Long roomId = message.getRoomId();
        
        switch (action) {
            case "START_GAME":
                webSocketRoomService.broadcastGameStarted(roomId);
                break;
            case "PLAY_CARD":
                // Handle card play
                break;
        }
    }
}
```

